textBeforeTable: Looking at Branden's Genworth Statistics for his most recent 20 rounds, he is tending to play the Par 4 holes very well, but is a little inconsistent on the Par 3 and Par 5 holes. Like St Andrews, Royal Durban has an abundance of Par 4's which may play into his hands.
